title: Bobby And Amy Sing Amy Grant’s Biggest Hits...TO HER...In Studio! + Fun Fact Friday Face-Off: Amy vs. Bae + Bobby Accepts Raymundo's TV Dare!
itunes:title: Bobby And Amy Sing Amy Grant’s Biggest Hits...TO HER...In Studio! + Fun Fact Friday Face-Off: Amy vs. Bae + Bobby Accepts Raymundo's TV Dare!
description:
Amy Grant stops by the studio to talk about her new big tour, 30th anniversary of her album and we talk to her (and sing back) about her biggest hits from the 90’s. Amy is undefeated as she takes on Raymundo’s wife “Bae” in the Fun Fact Friday Faceoff.
